lead_paragraph: Ulster's Iain Henderson and Tommy Bowe will miss Ireland's defence of their Six Nations title through injury, the province's coach and one of the players were quoted as saying on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Ireland's Henderson, Bowe Ruled Out of Six Nations
